{{Quote|Internal Affairs calls their field agents "keyns," after a renown ''sic'' tracking carnivore of the Gontzol system, ''&hellip;''.|An Imperial Intelligence report|<ref name="Imperial Sourcebook (Second Edition)">[[Imperial Sourcebook (Second Edition)|''Imperial Sourcebook'', Second Edition]]</ref>}}
